### Get Dashboard Statistics
### GET /dashboard/stats
### Returns statistics for the current user:
### - Tasks created by user
### - Tasks completed
### - Tasks near due date (within 3 days)
### - Tasks delayed (past due date)
### - Tasks in progress (assigned and accepted)
### - Tasks under review
### - Tasks pending acceptance
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### Response Example:
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "data": {
###     "tasksCreatedByUser": 10,
###     "tasksCompleted": 5,
###     "tasksNearDueDate": 3,
###     "tasksDelayed": 1,
###     "tasksInProgress": 2,
###     "tasksUnderReview": 1,
###     "tasksPendingAcceptance": 2
###   }
### }

